@VARS_CONSTANTS
FPS: number = 30 — standard frame rate
W: number = 1920 — standard width
H: number = 1080 — standard height

@INTERFACES
Scripts: { dev: "remotion studio" | render | build | typecheck | extract-glyphs }

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: src/ | scripts/ | skills/ | public/
external: remotion ^4 | @remotion/* ^4 | react ^19 | typescript ^5.4

@STANDARDS
- Path alias: @/* → src/*
- Fonts loaded in Root.tsx: Montserrat + IBM Plex Mono (latin-ext for Czech)
- Phosphor icon fonts loaded as side-effect from icons/loadPhosphorFont.ts
- All compositions registered in Root.tsx via <Composition>
